  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Fitbit
    This class will be used to get information from Fitbit services as well as calling for new tokens and saving data Consists of: Heart Statistics, Best and Lifetime Statistics, Daily Statistics and Goals
  • Class Summary

    Accolade_Node
    This class represents one accolade
    Accolades
    This class will be used to keep track of the accolade badges achieved by the user

    This is the main class that is run by the jar.

    This class will be used to modify and store best statistics

    This class implements the closable main tabs on the main window.

    This class will be used to modify and store daily statistics
